stdfs.conf\\&quot;&#39;&quot;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p>3.2 拷贝修改配置文件<br><code>cp mod_fastdfs.conf /etc/fdfs/</code><br><code>vi /etc/fdfs/mod_fastdfs.conf</code><br>修改内容</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"lang-java\">base_path=/fastdfs/fastdfs-nginx-module    基本路径，需提前创建\r\nuse_storage_id = true    是否使用id存储\r\nstorage_ids_filename = storage_ids.conf    storage_ids路径\r\ntracker_server=192.168.1.103:22122    tracker地址\r\nstorage_server_port=23000    storage端口\r\ngroup_name=group1    当前组名\r\nurl_have_group_name = true    url是否包含组名\r\nstore_path_count=1    存储地址个数\r\nstore_path0=/fastdfs/storage    storage存储地址\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p>3.3 拷贝文件<br>nginx启动报错<code>[ERROR - file:ini_file_reader.c,line:315,include file &quot;http.conf&quot; not ]</code><br>拷贝fastdfs安装包的文件<br><code>cp ~/fastDFS/fastdfs-5.11/conf/http.conf /etc/fdfs/</code><br><code>cp ~/fastDFS/fastdfs-5.11/conf/mime.types /etc/fdfs/</code></p>\r\n</li><li>安装nginx<br>4.1 安装依赖<code>yum -y install gcc pcre-devel zlib-devel openssl openssl-devel</code><br>4.2 安装nginx集成fastdfs-nginx-module<br><code>tar -xvf nginx-1.15.2.tar</code><br><code>cd nginx-1.15.2</code><br><code>./configure --add-module=/root/fastDFS/fastdfs-nginx-module-1.20/src/</code><br><code>make &amp;&amp; make install</code><br>4.3 配置nginx<br><code>vi /usr/local/nginx/conf/nginx.conf</code><br>修改内容<pre><code class=\"lang-java\">location /group1 {\r\n ngx_fastdfs_module;\r\n}\r\n</code></pre>\r\n4.4 启动nginx<br><code>cd /usr/local/</code><br><code>sbin/nginx -c conf/nginx.conf</code><br><code>sbin/nginx -s reload</code><h2 id=\"h2-u96C6u7FA4u914Du7F6E\"><a name=\"集群配置\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>集群配置</h2></li><li>tracker配置<br>与单机版一致，并且多台tracker可以一致<br>修改<code>/etc/fdfs/storage_ids.conf</code><br>修改内容<pre><code class=\"lang-java\"># &lt;id&gt;  &lt;group_name&gt;  &lt;ip_or_hostname&gt;\r\n100001   group1  192.168.1.104\r\n100002   group1  192.168.1.106\r\n100003   group2  192.168.1.107\r\n100004   group2  1